</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Beats X Stüssy 推限量版便攜式藍牙喇叭 Pill+ 原版外型配骷髏頭設計回歸</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/06/apple-resurrects-beats-pill-plus-in-limited-edition-collab/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-resurrects-beats-pill-plus-in-limited-edition-collab</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 05 Mar 2022 21:33:19 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[beats]]></category><category><![CDATA[Beats Pill+]]></category><category><![CDATA[Stüssy]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1088825</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前曾推出 Beats Pill+，但數個月前已經停產。但據外媒報導，Beats Pill+ 將再 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 早前曾推出 Beats Pill+，但數個月前已經停產。但據外媒報導，Beats Pill+ 將再次回歸，與時尚品牌 Stüssy 合作推出限量版款式。喇叭採用骷髏頭設計加上 Stüssy 的標誌，預計將於 3 月 4 日，開始發售。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1088826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.18.30-694x459.png" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.18.30-694x459.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.18.30-1280x846.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.18.30-768x507.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.18.30.png 1450w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 早於 2015 年，推出第一代 Beats Pill+，其尺寸較第一款 Beats Pill 稍大，也是 Apple 自 2014 年以 30 億美元收購 Beats 後發佈的首款喇叭。Pill+ 配有立體聲有源雙向分頻系統，高低音單元分離設計，內置咪高風及 12 小時續航力。是次推出的限量款式，在設計上採用 Stüssy 標誌性的南加州美學，以黑色調為基礎，在外側注入骷髏圖樣，內側則有品牌徽標，細節處還能看到底座的「The only good system is a sound system.」塗鴉字樣敘述。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1088827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.03-694x471.png" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.03-694x471.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.03-1280x869.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.03-768x522.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.03.png 1452w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1088828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.51-595x580.png" alt="" width="595" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.51-595x580.png 595w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.51-924x900.png 924w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.51-768x748.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-03-下午 5.19.51.png 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 595px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">該聯名款式預計在太平洋時間 3 月 4 日上午 10 時登陸 Stüssy 官網上架，售價為 $185 美元（約港幣 1441 元）。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/2/22958728/apple-beats-pill-speaker-stussy-sale-limited">The Verge</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
